title: Battle of the Titans: Warriors vs. Nets Preview | Real Ones
description:
Logan and Raja dive deep into this Tuesday’s battle between the Warriors and Nets in Brooklyn (0:30), including their impressions of the Nets so far this season (14:15), the differences between the two organizations (19:20), and much more analysis and player perspectives for this exciting matchup.
Hosts: Logan Murdock and Raja Bell
Associate Producer: Sasha Ashall
